Representatives from nonprofits highlight mission-driven career paths, and career counselors assist unsure students in identifying suitable industries. Alumni volunteers provide quick pep talks near the coffee station to support and encourage attendees. The dean visits to thank recruiters for their support of the university. At one booth, a robotics startup attracts attention by flying a small drone. As students exit the event, they carry tote bags filled with information, notebooks, and a stack of business cards. Later, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.
